   "season": [Season.WARM],
   "family": "Gramineae",
   "description": "Corn demands fertile soil, consistent moisture and warm weather. If you have those and plenty of garden space to spare, it’s not hard to grow great-tasting corn, and you won’t get it any fresher.",
